article_text:
Athens, TX (75751)

Today

Thunderstorms likely. A few storms may be severe. High 77F. Winds S at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 100%..

Tonight

Scattered thunderstorms during the evening. Cloudy skies after midnight. A few storms may be severe. Low 69F. Winds S at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 50%.
